\begin_inset Formula $(x,y)\mapsto\Vert x-y\Vert$
\end_inset

, y llamamos 
\begin_inset Formula $B_{X}\coloneqq B[0,1]=\overline{B(0,1)}=\{x\in X\mid\Vert x\Vert\leq1\}$
\end_inset

